tafsir[98]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"(Kaaf Haa Yaa Ayiin Saad) hari yewtanooma fii yeru majje ka fuﾉ遼熔ode Simoore Albaqara."
  19,2,"ﾆ隔m ko jaﾅ逆a Yurmeende Joomi maaﾉ預 nde O yurminiri jeyaaﾉ熔 Makko on Jakariyaa (yo o his), Meﾉ容n fillanomaa fii taskagol nde."
  19,3,"Tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi mako O Senike noddaandu suuﾉ擁indu fii yo ndu laato ﾉ砥rndu ﾉ殿daade jaabagol"
  19,4,"O maaki: ""Ko An Jooma, min dey ﾆｴi'e am ﾉ容n lo'ii, puri hoore am nden ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁i, mi wonaali sooyuﾉ熔 ka toragol Ma, ko woni, tuma kala mi toriMaa A jaabinanay lam."
  19,5,"Min dey mi hulii ﾉ殿dondiraaﾉ兎 am ﾉ兎n fii wata ﾉ兎 ronku daranaade Diina kan ﾉ殿awo mayde am sabu soklirdeﾉ兎 aduna, sonnaajo am on kadi laatike dimaro o jibintaa, okkan immorde ka Maaﾉ預 ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 walloowo."
  19,6,"O rona Annabaaku ngun e am o rona ngu kadi e ﾉ兎ynguure Yaaquuba nden (yo o his),o waﾉ蓉 mbo ko An yo Jooma- weltoraaﾉ熔 ka Diina makko e ka njikku makko e ganndal makko."
  19,7,"Alla jaabini toraare makko nden, O noddi mo: ""Ko an Jakariyaa, Menen Meﾉ容n humpitude ma ko weltinay maa, gomﾉ擁i Men jaabinii toraare maaﾉ預 nden, Men okkii ma suka innde makko ko Yahyaa, Men waﾉ預naali goﾉ遼熔 goo ado makko ndee innde""."
  19,8,"Jakariyaa maaki tawi ko o haawiiﾉ熔 kattanﾉ容 Alla ﾉ容n: ""Ko honno jibinirantee lam ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 sonnaajo am on ko dimaro o jibintaa? gomﾉ擁i mi hewtirii hattirnde ngurndan ﾉ預n sabu nayewu ngun e lo'ude ﾆｴi'e ﾉ容n."
  19,9,"Malaa'ikaajo on wi'i: ""Fiyaake on kono mi wi'iri non, fii kala sonnaajo maa on jiidotaako, an kadi a hewtii hattirde ngurndan ﾉ預n sabu nayewu ngun e lo'ere ﾆｴi'e ﾉ容n, kono Joomi maaﾉ預 Daalii: Tgugol Joomi maaﾉ預 Yahyaa immorde e neeniraawo dimaro e baabiraawo hewtuﾉ熔 hattirde ngurndan ﾉ預n ko newiiﾉ蓉m, gomﾉ擁i Mi Tagiino ma -an Jakariyaa- ko adii ﾉ蓉m hari a laataaki huunde jaﾅ逆eteende, sabu hari an ko a waasaaﾉ熔."
  19,10,"Jakariyaa maaki (yo o his): ""Ko an yo Jooma, waﾉ預nam maande nde miﾉ熔 deeﾆｴira sabu mun hara hinde tinndini e gasugol ko Malaa'ikaajo on weltiniri lam kon"". O Daali: ""Maande maaﾉ預 e gasugol ko weltiniraﾉ預a kon ko nde tawi a hattan-hattantaake wowlidude e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n balﾉ容 tati hara wanaa ﾃｱaw, ko woni, hara hiﾉ預 wonndi e cellal e aafiya""."
  19,11,"Jakariyaa yalti ka juulirde o acci yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n, o joopanii ﾉ兎 ko aldaa e haala: ""Subuhinanee Alla Seniiﾉ熔 On ka arannde ﾃｱallal e ka sakkitoode maggal."
  19,12,"Yahyaa jibinanaa mo, tuma nde o hewtunoo duuﾉ妬 yewtideede Men wi'ani mo: ""Ko an yo Yahyaa, jogitor Tawreeta on soobee e tinnaare, Men Okki mo ganndal e faamu e soobinaare e pellital tawi ko duuﾉ兎 suka o jogii."
  19,13,"Men Yurmini mo Yurmeende immrnde ka Amen, Men laﾉ橡妬ni mo e junuubu, o woni kuldo Alla ﾉ熔ftiiﾉ熔 Yamaruyee Alla on, himo woﾉ遼擁too haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n."
  19,14,"O laatike ﾉ擁gganﾉ熔 yumma makko e bem makko, newaniiﾉ熔 ﾉ兎, moﾆｴﾆｴotooﾉ熔 e maﾉ橡兎, o laataaki mawnintinaniiﾉ熔 ﾉ熔ftagol Joomi makko maa ﾉ熔ftagol neene e baaba, o wonaa yedduﾉ熔 Joomi makko maa yumma makko e bem makko."
  19,15,"Kisiyee e hoolaare immorde ka Alla wonii e makko ﾃｱalnde o jibinaa, e ﾃｱalnde o maayata o yalta e ﾉ預am ngurndan ﾉ熔o, e ﾃｱalnde o immintintee ko o wuuruﾉ熔 ﾉ蓉n ko ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, e ﾉ擁i nokuuli tati ko ﾉ擁n ﾉ砥ri wulﾉ擁nnde e ko neﾉ遼預nke rewata e mun, si o hoolike e ﾉ擁i, haray kulol fawaaki mo e nokkuuli goo."
  19,16,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ka Alqur'aanaare Tellinaande e maaﾉ預 kumpital fii Mariyama (yo o his) tuma nde o pottitinoo(deestino) yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n, o weddii e nukkuure hikkornde funnaange maﾉ橡兎."
  19,17,"O jogitanii hoore-makko gaanin yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n heedo wirnayngo mo haa tawa ﾉ兎 yi'ataa himo rewa Joomi makko, Men Nuli e makko Jibrila (yo o his), o nanndintinanii mo e mbaadi neﾉ遼預nke timmuﾉ熔 tagu, [Mariyama] huli wata taw ko faalaaﾉ熔 waﾉ蓉de mo ko boni."
  19,18,"Tuma nde o yi'unoo mo e mbaadi neﾉ遼預nke timmuﾉ熔 tagu himo fewti e makko, O maaki: ""Min miﾉ熔 fattoo Yurmiteeﾉ熔 On immorde e maaﾉ預 fii bone immorﾉ熔 e maaﾉ預 wota hewtam -ko an o'o - si a laatike hiﾉ預 hula Alla."
  19,19,"Jibrila (yo o his) wi'i: ""Min mi laataaki ﾉ殿nndinke, anndu min ko mi Nulaaﾉ熔 Joomi maaﾉ預 O Nulii lam e maaﾉ預 fii yo mi okke ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 moﾆｴﾆｴo laaﾉ砥ﾉ熔."
  19,20,"Mariyama maaki ko o haawiiﾉ熔: ""Ko honno woni- ranta lam ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 hara ﾉ殿daaki lam genndo wanaa tanaa mun, mi laataaki kadi jeenoowo sakko mi heﾉ殿 ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔?!"""
  19,21,"Jibriila wi'ani mo: ""Fiyaake on ko wano mi jaﾅ逆ori non, fii kala gorko meemaali ma wanaa tanaa mun a laataaki kadi jeenoowo, kono Joomi maaﾉ預 Senayee woananii Mo O Daalii: ""Tagugol ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 mo alaa baaba no newii e Makko, fii yo ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 mo okkaﾉ預a on laato maande wonannde yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e Kattanﾉ容 Alla, e Yurmeende Amen e maaﾉ預 e kala gomﾉ擁mﾉ熔 mo, Tagugol ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 maa on laatike ﾃ疎awoore immornde ka Alla eﾉ橡殿ande, winndaa- nde ka Alluwal Reenaangal""."
  19,22,"O roondii mo ﾉ殿awo wuttugol Malaa'ikaajo on, o pottitodi=deesti e makko faade e nokkuure woﾉ遼擁tiinde yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  19,23,"ﾅ蛎ta on fiﾉ擁 mo, sornoyi mo e mbinnde tamarohi, Mariyama (yo o his) wi'i: ""Ee hara nun mi maayuno ko adii ngal ﾃｱallal, mi wona huunde nde anndite-taake fii wota mi sikkitore bonke""."
  19,24,"Iisaa noddi mo ka ley koyﾉ容 makko: ""Wata a suno, gomﾉ擁i Joomi maaﾉ預 waﾉ擁i ley maaﾉ預 ilol ndiyam ngol yaarataa e mun"""
  19,25,"Jogito jullere tamarohi kin dimmbaa nde, nde saama ﾉ兎nnduﾉ容 ﾉ預ati teﾉ殿aﾉ容 e fewndo mun."
  19,26,"ﾃ疎amu e ﾉ兎nnduﾉ容, yaraa ndiyam ﾉ預m, weltinir wonkii kin sanfaajo(cukulel) maa on wata a suno, si a yi'ii goﾉ遼熔 e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n o lanndimaa kumpital fii sanfaajo on wi'an mo: ""Min dey mi waﾉ遼擁nii e wonkii am fii Joomi am deﾆｴﾆｴere gaayi haala, hannde mi yewtidataa gooto e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  19,27,"Mariyama ardi e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 makko on ka yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n himo tammbii mo, yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n wi'ani mo e hoore aﾃｱugol: ""Ko an yo Mariya, gomﾉ擁i a addii fiyaake mawﾉ熔 fefindaaﾉ熔, nokku ka arduﾉ預a e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 ko aldaa e baaba""."
  19,28,"Ko an yo nanndo Haaruuna ka dewal (on ko gorko moﾆｴﾆｴo) baaba maaﾉ預 wonaali jeenoowo, neene maaﾉ預 kadi wonaali jeenoowo, an ko a iwdi suudu laaﾉ砥ndu anndiraandu moﾆｴﾆｴugol, ko honno addirtaa ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 mo alaa baaba."
  19,29,"O sappii ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 makko on Iisaa (yo o his) tawi himo ka wooforndu, yimﾉ兎 [Mariyama] ﾉ兎n wi'ani mo hiﾉ殿 haawoo: ""Ko honno men yewtirta e boobo woofaaﾉ熔?!"""
  19,30,"Iisaa (yo o his) maaki: ""Min dey ko mi jeyaaﾉ熔 Alla, O Okkii lam Linnjiila, O Waﾉ擁 lam Annabaajo immorde e Annabaaﾉ兎 Makko."
  19,31,"O Waﾉ擁 lam heewuﾉ熔 nafa wonannde jeyaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n nokku kala ka mi laatii, O Yamiri lam tottugol Julde nden e Jonnugol Jakka on juudde ngurndam am."
  19,32,"O Waﾉ擁 lam ﾉ擁gganﾉ熔 Yumma am, O Waﾉ預ali lam mawnintinaniiﾉ熔 doftagol Joomi am, wanaa mi yeddoowo Mo."
  19,33,"Hoolaare e [bone] Seytaane e wallooﾉ兎 mo ﾉ兎n wonii e am ﾃｱalnde mi jibinanoo e ﾃｱalnde mi maayata e ﾃ疎lnde mi immintintee ko mi wuuruﾉ熔 ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, Seytaane foppaaki lam e nder ﾉ擁i nokkuuli tati wulﾉ擁nﾉ擁(njeewdi.)"
  19,34,"On siforaaﾉ熔 ﾉ擁n sifaaji ko kanko woni Iisaa geﾉ預l Mariyama, kaa haala ﾉ熔o ko ﾉ蓉m woni konngol Goongawol ngol e mu'un, wanaa ko majjuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'ata kon, ﾉ兎n sikkitotooﾉ兎 e fiyaake makko ﾉ兎 luutondira."
  19,35,"Haananaa Alla nde O jogitotoo ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔, O Laaﾉ妬i gaayi ﾉ蓉m O Senike, si O faandike huunde, pellet, yonay Mo Senayee wonanii Mo nde O Daalanta nden huunde: ""Wonu"", nde wona feere alaa, ko nii O woniri Kanko ko O Seniiﾉ熔 e gaayi ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔."
  19,36,"Pellet, Alla Senayee wonanii Mo ko Kanko woni Joomi am, ko Kanko kadi woni Joomi mo'on, laﾉ橡妬nanee Mo Dewal ngal Kanko Tun, ﾉ蓉m ko mi jaﾅ逆anii on ko ﾉ蓉m woni Laawol Focciingol ngol yottinayngol e Welayee Alla."
  19,37,"luutrii luutruﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fii fiyaake Iisaa (yo o his) ﾉ兎 luutondiri ﾉ兎 wonti feddeeji sertuﾉ擁 e hakkunde yimﾉ兎 makko, yoga maﾉ橡兎 gomﾉ擁ni ﾉ兎 wi'i: ""Ko o Nulaaﾉ熔"" woﾉ遼兎 goo yeddi mo wano Alyahuuda en, wano fedde goo yeewiri non e fii makko woﾉ遼兎 maﾉ橡兎 wi'i: ""Ko Kanko woni Alla"". Woﾉ遼兎 goo kadi wi'i: ""Ko o ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 Alla"". Alla Toowii gaayi ﾉ蓉m, bone wonanii ﾉ兎n luutondirﾉ兎 e fii fiyaake makko e taweede ﾃ疎lnde Darngal Mawngal sabu ko woni e maggal e seedafuyeeji e Hasboore e Lepte."
  19,38,"Kaawee ko nanirta wa maﾉ橡兎 nden ﾃｱalnde kaawee ko yi'irta wa maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 nanii fewndo nanﾉ容 nafataa ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 yi'ii fewndo giiﾉ容 nafataa ﾉ兎, kono tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka ngurndan aduna hiﾉ兎 e nder majjere ﾉ殿nngunde gaayi Laawol Focciingol ngol, ﾉ兎 alaa heblanaade Laakara on haa o ara e maﾉ橡兎 e juhayee hara kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 e hoore tooﾃｱe maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n."
  19,39,"Hulﾉ妬nir -an Nulaaﾉ熔- yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾃ疎lnde Nimse tuma nimsata bonnuﾉ熔 on e hoore bonnere makko nden, moﾆｴﾆｴinﾉ熔 on kadi [nimsa] anngal hibbingol makko ﾉ熔ftaare nden, tuma nde ﾉ容ri dewal ngal taggaa, hasboore maﾉ橡兎 nden timmi, gooto kala hikkondiri e ko o ardinnoo kon, hari kamﾉ兎 ka ngurndam maﾉ橡兎 aduna ko ﾉ兎 hoditorﾉ兎 ﾉ預m, ko ﾉ兎 welsindiiﾉ兎 fii Laakara, toode kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁naano ﾃ疎lnde Darngal."
  19,40,"Menen, ko Menen woni heddotooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ殿awo re'ugol tagoore nden, Men rona leydi ndin, Men ronira kadi ﾉ兎n wonuﾉ兎 e hoore mayri re'ugol ﾉ兎 e heddagol Amen ﾉ殿awo maﾉ橡兎, e Jeyal Amen e maﾉ橡兎, e firlitorgol Amen e maﾉ橡兎 no Men Yiﾉ擁ri, ko ka Amen Menen Tun ﾉ兎 ruttoytee ﾃ疎lnde Darngal fii Hasboore e Njoﾉ電i."
  19,41,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ka Alqur'aanaare Tellinaande e maaﾉ預 kumpital fii Ibraahiima (yo o his), pellet, konko o laatino heewuﾉ熔 Goonga e Goonginngol Aayeeje Alla ﾉ容n, ko o Annabaajo kadi immorde ka Alla."
  19,42,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko Aajara: ""Ko an yo baaba; ko honﾉ蓉n rewantaa gaanin Alla sanamuuru ndu nanataa noddaandu maaﾉ預 ndun si a noddii ndu, ndu yi'ataa dewal maaﾉ預 ngal si a rewii ndu, ndu ittantaa ma lorra, ndu pooﾉ預ntaa ma nafa."
  19,43,"Ko an yo baaba, min dey gomﾉ擁i arii e am immorde e Ganndal e laawol wahayu ko araali e maaﾉ預, jokkam mi fewne e Laawol Focciingol."
  19,44,"Ko an yo baaba, wata a ﾉ熔fto Seytaane rewaa mo, pellet, Seytaane laatike yedduﾉ熔 Hinnorante, nokku ka O Yamirnoo mo sujjanngol Aadama o sujjaali."
  19,45,"Ko an yo baaba, min dey miﾉ熔 huli wata Lepte heﾉ兎 immorde ka Hinnorante si a maayii e hoore keeferaaku maa ngun, laatoﾉ預a ﾉ殿diiﾉ熔 Seytaane ka Lepte sabu weldigal maaﾉ預 e makko."
  19,46,"Aajara wi'ani ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 makko on Ibraahiima (yo o his): ""Enee, an Ibraahiima a ﾉ蓉uroto ﾉ擁i sanamuuji am ﾉ擁 mi rawata?! pellet, si a tertaaki yennugol sanamji am ﾉ擁n mi fiﾉ擁rte kaaﾆｴe, seedu e am jamaanu juu-tungu wata a yewtam, wata a wonndu e am."
  19,47,"Ibraahiima (yo o his) maaki: ""Kisiyee e maaﾉ預 immorde e am, a heﾉ殿taa ko mettaymaa ko iwri e am, mi toranto ma haforaneede e peewal ka Joomi am, pellet, Kanko O Senike ko O heewuﾉ熔 Newanaade lam."
  19,48,"Mi seeda e mo'on mi seeda kadi e ﾉ擁n reweteeﾉ擁 mon ﾉ擁 rewoton ﾉ蓉m gaanin Alla. Mi toroo Joomi am Kanko Tun mi kafidataa Mo e huunde, no gasa O salantaako lam si mi torike Mo, mi laatoo malkisaaﾉ熔 sabu toragol Mo."
  19,49,"Tuma nde o accidunooﾉ兎 e reweeteeﾉ擁 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 woni rewude ﾉ擁n gaanin Alla, Men lontinani mo e hattagol yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n Men Okki mo ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 makko on Ishaaqa, Men Okki mo taniraawo makko on Yaaquuba, Men waﾉ擁 gooto kala e maﾉ橡兎 Annabaajo."
  19,50,"Men Okki ﾉ兎 e Yurmeende Amen wonndude e Annabaaku ngun moﾆｴﾆｴere ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉nde, Men waﾉ預ni ﾉ兎 mantoore moﾆｴﾆｴere jokkondirnde e ﾉ容nﾉ容 jeyaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  19,51,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ka Alqur'aanaare Tellinaande e maaﾉ預 kabaaru fii Muusaa (yo o his), kanko o woniino Suﾉ殿aﾉ熔 Siiwaa, o woniino kadi Nulaaﾉ熔 Annabaajo."
  19,52,"Men noddi mo ka senngo ﾃｱaamo fello ngon wonnannde nokkuure Muusaa nden (yo o his), Men ﾉ殿nni mo gunndeteeﾉ熔, nokku ka Alla nanini mo Daalol Makko ngol."
  19,53,"Men Okki [Muusaa] -immorde e Yurmeende Amen e Neeminngol Amen e makko- musiﾉ遼熔 makko on Haaruuna (yo o his); ka jaabinngol toraare makko nden fewndo o torinoo Joomi makko ﾉ蓉m."
  19,54,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ka Alqur'aanaare Tellinaande e maaﾉ預 kumpital fii Ismaa'iila (yo o his), kanko o woniino Goonguﾉ熔 fodoore, o fodataa fodoore si wonaa o humnii ndi, o woniino kadi Nulaaﾉ熔 Annabaajo."
  19,55,"O laatino himo yamira yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ﾃｱimnugol Julde nden, e tottugol Jakka on, o laatino kadi ka Joomi makko weltoraaﾉ熔."
  19,56,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ka Alqur'aanaare Tellinaande e maaﾉ預 kumpital fii Idriisa (yo o his), pellet, kanko o laatino heewuﾉ熔 Goonga e Goonginngol Aayeeje Joomi makko ﾉ容n, o laatino kadi Annabaajo jeyaa- ﾉ熔 e Annabaaﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎n."
  19,57,"Men ﾉ殿nti jaﾅ逆a makko on sabu ko Men Okki mo kon immorde e Annabaaku, o laatii toowuﾉ熔 darja."
  19,58,"ﾆ‘n jaﾅ逆aaﾉ兎 e nder ndee simoore, joﾅ喫 e Jakariyaa joofi e Idriisa (yo ﾉ兎 his), ko ﾉ兎n woni ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 Alla Neeminiri e mu'un Annabaaku ka ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 Aadama (yo o his), e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 Me njol-nunoka laana e bibbe Ibhiima e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 Yaaquuba (yo ﾉ兎 his), e ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 Men hawrinndiniri peewal faade e Lislaamu, Men Suﾉ妬 ﾉ兎 Men waﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 Annabaaﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 laatinoke si ﾉ兎 nanii Aayeeje Alla ﾉ容n no janngee ﾉ兎 sujjanay Alla ko ﾉ兎 wullooﾉ兎 sabu kulol Makko."
  19,59,"Aroyi ﾉ殿awo ﾉ兎e Annabaaﾉ兎 Suﾉ殿aﾉ兎 ﾉ熔o, [woﾉ橡兎 goo] jokkuﾉ兎 bone e majjere, ﾉ兎 yeebi Julde nden, ﾉ兎 addiraali nde no haaniri non, ﾉ兎 waﾉ遼擁tii ko wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n lokaa kon e geddi ﾉ擁n wano jeeno, aray ﾉ兎 hawroya e bone e taﾆｴaare ka Jahannama."
  19,60,"Si wonaa on tuubuﾉ熔 immorde e raﾉ橡妬nﾉ擁naare makko e fantingol makko, o gomﾉ擁ni Alla o golli golle moﾆｴﾆｴe, ﾉ兎n sifaaﾉ兎 ﾉ擁i sifaaji ﾉ熔o ﾉ兎 naatoya Aljanna on, hara ﾉ兎 uytantaake hay e huunde e njoﾉ電i golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, hay sinno fanﾉ擁i."
  19,61,"Aljannaaji ﾃｱiiﾉ殿l, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 Hinnorante Fodi jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka wirnii wonnde O naaday ﾉ兎 e nder majji, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 yi'aali ﾉ擁 kono ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁nii ﾉ擁, Alla Fodii Aljanna on -fii kala ko o wirniiﾉ熔- o aray feere woo alaa."
  19,62,"ﾆ‘ nanataa nder ton haalaaji puyﾉ擁, wonaa haalaaji bonﾉ擁, ko woni, hiﾉ兎 nana salminaango yoga maﾉ橡兎 e dow yoga, e salminaango Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e dow maﾉ橡兎, no ara e maﾉ橡兎 nder ton ko ﾉ兎 lokaa(wooﾉ預) kon immorde e ﾃｱaametee bimmbi e kiikiiﾉ容."
  19,63,"Oo Aljanna siforaaﾉ熔 ﾉ擁i sifaaji ko kanko woni on mo Men Roninta ﾉ蓉m immorde e jeyaaﾉ兎 Amen ﾉ兎n, on doftiiﾉ熔 Yamaruyeeji ﾉ擁n o woﾉ遼擁tiiﾉ熔 haﾉ預aﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n."
  19,64,"Wi'an -an Jibriila- Muhammadu (yo Alla Juulu e makko O hisna mo): pellet, Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 jippantaako hoore-maﾉ橡兎, anndu ko ﾉ兎 jipporta ko e Yamaruyee Alla, ko Alla heeranii ko men jaﾉ橡登to kon immorde e fiyaake Laakara, e ko men acci ﾉ蓉m immorde e fiyaake aduna, e kon ko woni hakkunde aduna e Laakara, Joomi maaﾉ預 wonaali -an Nulaaﾉ熔- yejjitoowo huunde."
  19,65,"Taguﾉ熔 On kammuuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin, e Jeyﾉ熔 ﾉ擁 On e Fewjoowo fii majji, e Taguﾉ熔 On ko woni kon hakkunde majji e Jeyﾉ熔 ﾉ蓉m e Fewjoowo fii mun On, ko On Hanndi e Reweede, tabitu e Dewal Makko, laatanaaki Mo yeruujo wanaa kadi ﾉ擁mmo mo no kafida e Makko ka Dewal."
  19,66,"Keefeero yedduﾉ熔 immital on no wi'a; ka jalnorgol: ""Eyoo, e jaka si mi maayii aroyay nde mi yaltinee ka qaburu am ko mi wuuruﾉ熔 ngurndam ﾉ擁mmal?! Pellet, ﾉ蓉m ko woﾉ遼蓉ﾉ蓉m."
  19,67,"Enee, hara oo yedduﾉ熔 Immital annditaali wonnde Menen Men Tagiino mo ko adii hari o laataaki hay e huunde?! O dallinora Tagu aranu ngun e dow Tagu ﾉ擁ﾉ預bu ngun, ko fii pellet, ko Tagu ﾉ擁ﾉ預bu ngun ﾉ砥ri welude fii e newaade."
  19,68,"Mi woondirii Joomi maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- Men yaltinoyay ﾉ兎 ka genaale maﾉ橡兎 faade ka Mofturu ko ﾉ兎 wonnduﾉ兎 e Seytanuuji maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ擁n majju-nooﾉ擁 ﾉ兎, refti Men soggoya ﾉ兎 faade ka dammbu-ﾉ容 Jahannama ko ﾉ兎 hoyﾉ兎, jicciriiﾉ兎 e koppi maﾉ橡兎."
  19,69,"Refti Men foodirabe no saﾉ葉iri e no boniri immorde e kala fedde e feddeeji majjere ﾉ擁n ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 ﾉ兎 saﾉ葉u- de geddi, ﾉ兎n ko yeesooﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n."
  19,70,"Refti ko Menen ﾆ「ri Anndunde ﾉ兎n ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 foddude naatugol yiite ngen e sonnjorgol nguleendi magge e tampirgol ndi."
  19,71,"Alaa e mooﾉ蓉n -ko onon yo yimﾉ兎- hay e gooto si wonaa o lummbay dow [ﾆｳanngal] Siraate waﾉ預-ngal ka fonngo Jahannama, ngollummbugol laatike ﾃ疎awoore Siinaande nde Alla ﾃ疎awi ﾉ蓉m, firtoowo ﾃ疎awoore Makko nden alaa."
  19,72,"Refti ﾉ殿awo ngol lummbugol Siraate Men Hisina ﾉ兎n hulirnooﾉ兎 Joomi mu'un ﾉ熔ftagol Yamiraaﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n e woﾉ遼擁tagol haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n, Men ﾉ預la tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko ﾉ兎 jicciiﾉ兎 e hoore koppi maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 hattantaake dogugol nge."
  19,73,"Si janngaama e dow yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Aayeeje Amen ﾆ∥nnguﾉ容 jippinaaﾉ容 ﾉ容n e Nulaaﾉ兎 Amen ﾉ兎n; yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'ana gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n: ""Ko hennde e feddeeji me'en ﾉ擁n ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude hoﾉ熔 e ﾃｱiiﾉ妬rnde, ﾉ砥ri fotude kadi mbatu e kawtital: ""Ko fedde Amen nden, kaa ko fedde mo'on nden?!""."
  19,74,"Kaawes ko ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁ri wa moftaaji ﾉ擁 Men halki ﾉ蓉m ko adii ﾉ兎e heeferﾉ兎 wasorayﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 woni kon e mu'un immorde e toowal yi'eteengal, ﾉ擁n moftaaji no ﾉ砥ri ﾉ兎 jawle, ﾉ砥ri ﾉ兎 kadi moﾆｴﾆｴugol mbaadi sabu labeede conci maﾉ橡兎, e neemagol ﾉ殿lli maﾉ橡兎."
  19,75,"Maaku -an Nulaaﾉ熔-: ""On laatiiﾉ熔 no yinoo e nder majjere aray Hinnorante nennana mo haa o ﾉ兎y- doo majjere, haa si ﾉ兎 yi'ii ko ﾉ兎 wonanoo fodeede kon immorde e lepte yaccinaaﾉ容 ﾉ容n ka aduna, maaﾉ蓉m nennaaﾉ容 ﾉ容n haa ﾃ疎lnde Darngal aray ﾉ兎 annda ontuma ko hommbo boni nokku ﾉ砥ri fanﾉ蓉de wallooﾉ兎, e hara ﾉ蓉m ko fedde maﾉ橡兎 nden, kaa ko fedde gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n?"
  19,76,"E mbattiigu nennangol ﾉ兎eﾉ熔o haa ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎ydoo majjere, Alla no ﾉ兎ydana ﾉ兎ya feewuﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁nal e doftaare. Golle moﾆｴﾆｴe yottinayﾉ容 ﾉ容n e malal paamayankowal ngal ko ﾉ容n ﾉ砥ri nafa ka Joomi maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- njoﾉ電i, ko ﾉ蓉m kadi ﾉ砥ri battane."
  19,77,"Enee, a yi'aali -an Nulaaﾉ熔- on yedduﾉ熔 hujjaaji Amen ﾉ擁n, o yeddi Kammbaaji Amen ﾉ擁n, o wi'i: ""Si mi maayii, mi immintinoyaama maatun mi okkee jawdi ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ndi e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎""."
  19,78,"Enee, o anndu ko wirnii kon si o wi'i ko o wi'i kon no ﾉ殿nngiri?! Kaa o ﾆｴettodii e Joomi makko aadi fii yo O naadu mo Aljanna, O okkoya mo ton jawdi e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎?!"
  19,79,"Fiyaake on wanaa no o aaﾆｴori non, aray Men winnda ko o woni wowlude kon e ko o woni gollude kon, Men ﾉ兎ydana mo Lepte e dow lepte makko ﾉ容n, sabu ko o nodditii kon immorde e meere nden."
  19,80,"Men Rona ko o acci kon immorde e jawdi e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 ﾉ殿awo Men halkii mo, o ara e Amen ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ko o weddiiﾉ熔 hara o ﾉ登oraama ko o wonunoo dakmitorde kon immorde e jawdi e jaahu."
  19,81,"Sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n jogitii hoore-maﾉ橡兎 reweteeﾉ兎 gaanin Alla; fii yo ﾉ兎n laatano ﾉ兎 sembinooﾉ兎 e wallooﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 foolira sabu maﾉ橡兎."
  19,82,"Fiyaake on wanaa no ﾉ兎 aaﾆｴori non, ﾉ擁i reweteeﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 rewata ﾉ蓉m gaanin Alla, ﾉ擁 yeddoyay ﾃ疎lnde Darngal dewal ngal sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n rewunooﾉ擁 ngal, ﾉ擁 woﾉ遼擁too e maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ擁 laatanoo ﾉ兎 ayﾉ兎."
  19,83,"Enee, a yi'aali -an Nulaaﾉ熔- wonnde Menen Men nulii Seytanuuji ﾉ擁n, Men wurtiﾉ擁 e dow heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n hiﾉ擁 ﾆｴuunaﾉ兎 e waﾉ蓉gol geddi ﾉ擁n e faddagol ka Diina Alla e ﾆｴuunugol."
  19,84,"Wata a heﾃｱor -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬rgol Alla yaccin- gol halkugol ﾉ兎, anndu Men limay ﾉ兎 woni nguur- ndan maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ預m limugol, haa si haﾉ葉ii dummunne nennangol ﾉ兎 Men lepta ﾉ兎 yeru ko ﾉ兎 hanndi kon."
  19,85,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, ﾃ疎lnde Men mooﾉ登yta hulirooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Joomi mu'un -ﾉ熔ftagol Yamiraaﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n e woﾉ遼擁tagol Haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n- ka Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ko ﾉ兎 jamaa teddinaaﾉ熔."
  19,86,"Men sogga heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n haa ka Jahannama ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔nﾉ預aﾉ兎."
  19,87,"ﾆ‘e heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 maraa tefanngol woﾉ橡兎 maﾉ橡兎 si wonaa on jogtaninooﾉ熔 Alla aadi ka aduna fii gom- ﾉ擁nngol Mo e Nulaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n."
  19,88,"Alyahuuda en e Annasaaraa en e woﾉ橡兎 e sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'i: "" Hinnorante jogitike ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔""."
  19,89,"Gomﾉ擁i on addii -ko onon wowlooﾉ兎 ﾉ擁i- huunde mawnunde."
  19,90,"Kammuuli ﾉ擁n no ﾉ殿doo seekaade immorde e ngol konngol aﾃｱaangol, leydi ndin no ﾉ殿doo seekaade, pelle ﾉ容n no do'a yanude muncoo."
  19,91,"ﾆ隔m fow,ko sabu ko ﾉ兎 dammbani(askitina) kon Hinnorante ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔, Alla Toowii e ﾉ蓉m Toowal mawngal."
  19,92,"Gasataa nde Hinnorante jogitotoo ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 Senaade wonanii Mo e ﾉ蓉m."
  19,93,"Alaa wonﾉ熔 ka kammuuli e ka leydi immorde e Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e jinnaaji ﾉ擁n si wanaa o aroyay ka Joomi makko ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ko o yankiniiﾉ熔."
  19,94,"Gomﾉ擁i O Huﾉ妬ndorii ﾉ兎 Ganndal,o limibe limgol, suuﾉ預aki e Makko immorde e maﾉ橡兎 hay e huunde."
  19,95,"Gooto kala e maﾉ橡兎 aroy ka Makko ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ko o weddiiﾉ熔 hara o maraa ballo o maraa jawdi."
  19,96,"Pellet, ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎 golli golleeji moﾆｴﾆｴi weltoraaﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n ka Alla, Alla waﾉ預nay ﾉ兎 Giggol sabu Giggol Makko e maﾉ橡兎, e waﾉ蓉gol ﾉ兎 yiﾉ預aﾉ兎 ka jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n."
  19,97,"Anndu ko Men niwinani ndee Alqur'aanaare Jippinngol nde ka ﾉ容nngal maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ko fii yo a weltinir nde hulooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n , ﾉ兎n no ﾉ熔ftoo Yamiraaﾉ擁 Am ﾉ擁n, ﾉ兎 woﾉ遼擁too haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Am ﾉ擁n, hulﾉ妬niraa nde kadi yimﾉ兎 ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 saﾉ葉ude wennje e mawnintinaare e jaﾉ砥gol Goonga."
  19,98,"No foti hewde e moftaaji ﾉ擁 Men halki ﾉ蓉m ado yimﾉ兎 maaﾉ預 ﾉ兎n, taw si hiﾉ預 so'a hannde goﾉ遼熔 e ﾉ擁n moftaaji?! Taw si hiﾉ預 nananaﾉ兎 hito suuﾉ擁i- ngo?! Ko heﾉ妬 ﾉ兎 kon no tijjaa nde heﾉ妬 tanaa maﾉ橡兎 kadi tuma Alla sakkiti."
